@node "History" "Historique du programme"
@{b}44.6@{ub} (20.8.2001)

 - Added greyscale JPEG output mode.
 - Added TIFF fax options.
 - Added PNG alpha channel mode selector.
 - Corrected default PNG image gamma value (was 0.5 - now 0.45455).
 - Now uses less stack.

@{b}44.5@{ub} (31.7.2001)

 - Added support for WarpTIFF.
 - Recompiled with VBCC 0.8.

@{b}44.4a@{ub} (27.5.2001)

 - Added portuguÍs catalog and documentation.

@{b}44.4@{ub} (16.5.2001)

 - Thanks to the ATO, who have provided language support for czech,
   deutsch, espaŮol, franÁais, italiano, norsk, polski, russian, srpski
   and tŁrkÁe, including locale catalogs and installer translations.
 - Was forced to reorganize the window layout slightly, to make all the
   keyboard shortcuts work correctly.

@{b}44.3@{ub} (4.4.2001)

 - Added "Test" button, which allows you to adjust and try settings
   without closing the window and reloading WarpDTPrefs each time.
 - Added output mode and colour reduction settings for WarpJPEG 44.19.
 - Added gamma correction settings for WarpPNG 44.14.
 - Added support for WarpPSD.
 - Added pen selection settings.
 - Fixed visual corruption which occurred if gadgets were updated in a
   page that wasn't frontmost.

@{b}44.2@{ub} (18.3.2001)

 - Fixed problem with the dither gadgets not getting ghosted on startup
   if the dither override setting was set to "Nothing".
 - The installer wasn't copying the WarpDT icon - fixed.

@{b}44.1@{ub} (15.3.2001)

 - First release.
@endnode

